    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Jan 3, 2017</title>
      <link>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-01-03/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Jan 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-01-03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Be Prepared for Many More Data Breaches This Year&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There have been nearly 2,300 confirmed cases of data breaches in 2016, according to a Verizon report. This number will continue to increase as more &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cxotoday.com/story/be-prepared-for-many-more-data-breaches-this-year/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cxotoday.com/story/be-prepared-for-many-more-data-breaches-this-year/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What to do if your data is taken hostage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The plan identifies the organisation&amp;rsquo;s recovery time objective (RTO), and recovery point objective (RPO) for data breaches. In the event that a back-up &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.techcentral.ie/data-taken-hostage/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.techcentral.ie/data-taken-hostage/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The News of 2016: The Year in Review&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; and cellular providers, would have to get customer consent when using their data and report the use of that data as well as data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://newsbreaks.infotoday.com/NewsBreaks/The-News-of-2016-The-Year-in-Review-115278.asp&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://newsbreaks.infotoday.com/NewsBreaks/The-News-of-2016-The-Year-in-Review-115278.asp&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Guest post: New EU data protection regulations are on the way; are you&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Digital By Default News With ever more sophisticated attempts to hack both public and private companies, large scale data breaches are hitting the headlines on a regular &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.digitalbydefaultnews.co.uk/2017/01/03/guest-post-new-eu-data-protection-regulations-are-on-the-way-are-you-ready/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.digitalbydefaultnews.co.uk/2017/01/03/guest-post-new-eu-data-protection-regulations-are-on-the-way-are-you-ready/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How Advanced Analytics Can Shore Up Defenses Against Data Theft&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It can vastly improve an organization&amp;rsquo;s defense against cybersecurity threats, data breaches and privacy violations. An enterprise cybersecurity &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-management.com/news/security/how-advanced-analytics-can-shore-up-defenses-against-data-theft-10030595-1.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-management.com/news/security/how-advanced-analytics-can-shore-up-defenses-against-data-theft-10030595-1.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches through wearables put target squarely on IoT in 2017&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches through wearables put target squarely on IoT in 2017. Security needs to be baked into IoT devices for there to be any chance of halting &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.csoonline.com/article/3150881/internet-of-things/data-breaches-through-wearables-put-target-squarely-on-iot-in-2017.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.csoonline.com/article/3150881/internet-of-things/data-breaches-through-wearables-put-target-squarely-on-iot-in-2017.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cyber criminals to change tactics and charge higher ransoms in 2017&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While ransomware attacks and data breaches are set to grow this year, Ward expects that &amp;lsquo;breach fatigue&amp;rsquo; will set in amongst the general public, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.businessworld.ie/technology-news/Cyber-criminals-to-change-tactics-and-charge-higher-ransoms-in-2017-567060.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.businessworld.ie/technology-news/Cyber-criminals-to-change-tactics-and-charge-higher-ransoms-in-2017-567060.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo Customer Database Unaffected By Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Two data breaches in the past appear not to have impacted traffic on Yahoo as users continue to use its services and numbers remain roughly steady, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/yahoo-customer-database-unaffected-by-breaches-/d/d-id/1327815&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/yahoo-customer-database-unaffected-by-breaches-/d/d-id/1327815&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Failing to Prepare is Preparing to Fail with Network Security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a particular concern in the payment card industry, for example, where data breaches can mean compromising data from millions of credit cards.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/opinions/failing-to-prepare-network-security/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/opinions/failing-to-prepare-network-security/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Top 5 Events of 2016 and Their Impact on the FinTech Industry in 2017&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s Data Breach: Yahoo had not one but two record data breaches announced this year, both of which took place over two years ago. They are &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.paymentsjournal.com/PressRelease.aspx?id=34141&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.paymentsjournal.com/PressRelease.aspx?id=34141&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;2016: A year of cyber lessons  Dr John McCarthy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches will now incur serious fines and organisations will now need to appoint data processors and controllers to ensure compliance to the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.internationalairportreview.com/26200/airport-extra/2016-year-cyber-security-lessons/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.internationalairportreview.com/26200/airport-extra/2016-year-cyber-security-lessons/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Ransomware to Emerge as Gravest Security Threat In 2017&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;IT security is moving towards big data and analytics, especially in areas such as threat hunting where it is becoming increasingly difficult to interrogate &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-management.com/news/security/ransomware-to-emerge-as-gravest-security-threat-in-2017-10030596-1.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-management.com/news/security/ransomware-to-emerge-as-gravest-security-threat-in-2017-10030596-1.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hostile Takeovers And Cyber Breaches Have One Thing In Common&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skroupa: Given how data breaches and loss of confidential information can negatively affect shareholder value and senior executives&amp;rsquo; reputations, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.forbes.com/sites/christopherskroupa/2017/01/03/hostile-takeovers-and-cyber-breaches-have-one-thing-in-common/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.forbes.com/sites/christopherskroupa/2017/01/03/hostile-takeovers-and-cyber-breaches-have-one-thing-in-common/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Guest column: The cloud isn&amp;rsquo;t as secure as you may think&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over the last several years, companies like Yahoo, Google, LinkedIn and Facebook have experienced major data breaches. So have presumably &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/news/science/sd-me-guestcolumn-cloud-20170103-story.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/news/science/sd-me-guestcolumn-cloud-20170103-story.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;draft-ietf-pals-endpoint-fast-protection-05&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;from CE1 to CE2 over PW1, this scenario is the same as the scenario shown in &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-pals-endpoint-fast-protection-05&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-pals-endpoint-fast-protection-05&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Massachusetts makes data breach reports available online&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hundreds of data breaches affecting thousands of Massachusetts residents were reported to the state in 2016. The Office of Consumer Affairs and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.sacbee.com/news/business/technology/article124320004.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.sacbee.com/news/business/technology/article124320004.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo data breaches unlikely to sink Verizon deal, Bloomberg finds&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to the San Diego, Calif.-based Identity Theft Resource Center, nearly 1,000 data breaches, including Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s, occurred in the U.S. in 2016, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itbusiness.ca/news/yahoo-data-breaches-unlikely-to-sink-verizon-deal-bloomberg-finds/85074&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itbusiness.ca/news/yahoo-data-breaches-unlikely-to-sink-verizon-deal-bloomberg-finds/85074&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breach info now available online&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Citizens and reporters looking for information on data breaches no longer have to go through the formal and sometimes protracted public records &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.salemnews.com/news/data-breach-info-now-available-online/article_4b0e791e-d1f0-11e6-ba18-93bee4254d1d.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.salemnews.com/news/data-breach-info-now-available-online/article_4b0e791e-d1f0-11e6-ba18-93bee4254d1d.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Massachusetts makes data breach reports available online&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches reported in 2016 affected anywhere from a single resident to thousands. The largest number involved breach of credit card numbers, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bostonherald.com/news/local_coverage/2017/01/massachusetts_makes_data_breach_reports_available_online&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bostonherald.com/news/local_coverage/2017/01/massachusetts_makes_data_breach_reports_available_online&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;LANDESK, HEAT to combine as LANDESK is purchased by HEAT owner&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; solution, before that acquisition, was highlighted by its strong security features, including patching, security suite, and endpoint protection.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.channelbuzz.ca/2017/01/landesk-heat-to-combine-as-landesk-is-purchased-by-heat-owner-19877/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.channelbuzz.ca/2017/01/landesk-heat-to-combine-as-landesk-is-purchased-by-heat-owner-19877/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches packed a weaker punch in Mass. in 2016. Here are the firms&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Boston Business Journal The number of Massachusetts residents affected by data breaches last year fell to its lowest level since state regulators began collecting information &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bizjournals.com/boston/news/2017/01/03/data-breaches-packed-a-weaker-punch-in-mass-in.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bizjournals.com/boston/news/2017/01/03/data-breaches-packed-a-weaker-punch-in-mass-in.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Public apathy on online security &amp;lsquo;exploited&amp;rsquo; by cyber criminals&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That is the prediction of leading Irish information security company, Ward Solutions, which said that &amp;lsquo;ransomware&amp;rsquo; attacks and data breaches are set to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.irishexaminer.com/business/public-apathy-on-online-security-exploited-by-cyber-criminals-437596.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.irishexaminer.com/business/public-apathy-on-online-security-exploited-by-cyber-criminals-437596.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
